des:
Ask for Profound Thoughts and learn the coolest thoughts from famous personalities till date.

To start, just say "Alexa, launch Profound Thoughts" or "Alexa, open Profound Thoughts" to get a new Profound thought".

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
